        <p>Despite trailing Competitor C on gross margin, our EBITDA margin leads the peer set by 330bps due to superior operational efficiency (S&amp;M 180bps below average). R&amp;D intensity (14.2%) exceeds industry norms, supporting the innovation-led growth thesis. Scale disadvantage vs. Competitor A ($55M gap) is the primary structural challenge.</p>

